    <b>NARRATIVE
    & DESIGN</b>

    <b>Stefania</b>

    <i>Story & Dialogue</i>


    <b>Mimi</b>

    <i>Game
    Design</i>


    <voffset=2em>

    <b>SPECIAL THANKS</b>

    Our Playtesters

    Coffee

    And
    You!

    </align>'
